[35m## [m[35mMonitoring and Observability[m

The platform includes [1m**Prometheus**[m and [1m**Grafana**[m for monitoring:

[38;5;130m-[m [1m**Prometheus**[m collects metrics from Docker containers and hosts.
[38;5;130m-[m [1m**Grafana**[m visualizes metrics via preconfigured dashboards.

Access Grafana at [35m`[mhttp://<manager-ip>:3000[35m`[m with default credentials [35m`[madmin:admin[35m`[m.

[35m## [m[35mSecrets Management[m

[38;5;130m-[m Sensitive information (e.g., database passwords, JWT secrets) is managed using [1m**Docker secrets**[m.
[38;5;130m-[m All sensitive data is injected securely into containers during runtime.

[35m---[m

[35m## [m[35mTroubleshooting[m

